Relations Across the Taiwan Straits (ARATS), said today that ARATS
plans to propose a meeting between Chinese President Jiang Zemin
and Koo Chen-fu, Chairman of the Taiwan Straits Exchange
Foundation (SEF), during the latter's visit to Beijing in
