The Angolan president said this while meeting with Chinese
Ambassador to Luanda Xiao Sijin at the State House here.
</P>
<P>
President Dos Santos said that he will go to visit China at
the invitation of Chinese President Jiang Zemin as scheduled in
mid-October.
</P>
<P>
