would be presented to George Graham for his opinion. But this is
purely hypothetical at the moment."
</P>
<P>
Ridsdale told the Yorkshire Post that Sugar had behaved like a
"perfect gentleman" and he said he was looking forward to having
lunch with him on Saturday. 
