<P>
"Having gone to watch my son play and having left the ground
without any problems, I am shocked and angry about the reports."
</P>
<P>
"The situation demands that the media informs its readers of
the truth and apologizes to Newcastle, Rotherham and both clubs'
fans as well as to my family."
</P>
<P>
Dalglish parted company with Newcastle United on August 27
after 19 months in charge at St James's Park and is currently
fighting a compensation battle with his former employers. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
