<HEADLINE> Brazilian President Vows to Defend National Currency </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRASILIA, September 23 (Xinhua) -- Brazilian President Fernando
Henrique Cardoso vowed on Wednesday to defend the stability of the
national currency, the real, in face of financial crisis in
southeast Asia and Russia.
</P>
<P>
