<HEADLINE> Ningbo to Offer Air Route to Taiwan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NINGBO, September 24 (Xinhua) -- Ningbo, a major port city in
east China's Zhejiang Province, will introduce an air route to the
Taiwan cities of Taipei and Kaohsiung on October 11, 1998.
</P>
<P>
Airbus A320 and A321 airlines leased from Macao Airlines will
be used for the weekly Tuesday and Saturday flights between
Zhejiang and Taiwan via Macao.
</P>
<P>
