<HEADLINE> Brazil Reports Large Outflow of Capital </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
RIO DE JANEIRO, September 23 (Xinhua) -- Brazil has lost 28.6
billion U.S. dollars from its national reserves since early August
1998, the newspaper O Jornal do Brasil reported Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
