on a wide range of issues of international concern, including the
complete prohibition and thorough destruction of nuclear weapons,
the impact of the East Asian financial crisis, the Middle East
peace process and the situation in Kosovo, the Federal Republic of
Yugoslavia. (UN-China-Speech) 
