<BODY>
<HEADLINE> French PM Arrives in Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 24 (Xinhua) -- French Prime Minister Lionel
Jospin arrived here this morning for a three-day official visit to
China at the invitation of Chinese Premier Zhu Rongji.
</P>
<P>
Chinese Vice-Foreign Minister Wang Yingfan and Chinese
Ambassador to France Cai Fangbai welcomed him at the airport.
</P>
<P>
It is learnt that Zhu will preside over a welcoming ceremony
for Jospin and hold talks with him later today. 
</P>
